749
00:38:26,763 --> 00:38:28,556
you fatuous nincompoop!

750
00:38:29,766 --> 00:38:32,477
Order!

751
00:38:33,312 --> 00:38:35,480
Procedure, Mr. Speaker.

752
00:38:35,731 --> 00:38:37,190
Mr. Wood has the floor.

753
00:38:37,274 --> 00:38:38,649
Instruct us,

754
00:38:38,734 --> 00:38:40,234
oh, Great Commoner.

755
00:38:40,319 --> 00:38:42,737
What is unnatural, in your opinion?

756
00:38:43,113 --> 00:38:45,114
Niggrahs casting ballots?

757
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:46,782
Niggrah representatives?

758
00:38:46,909 --> 00:38:48,910
Is that natural, Stevens?

759
00:38:49,328 --> 00:38:50,828
Intermarriage?

760
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:54,123
What violates natural law?

761
00:38:54,291 --> 00:38:56,834
Slavery and you.

762
00:38:57,503 --> 00:38:59,921
Pendleton, you insult God!

763
00:39:01,924 --> 00:39:03,174
You unnatural noise.

764
00:39:08,096 --> 00:39:10,431
Mr. Colfax, please, use your gavel!

765
00:39:10,766 --> 00:39:12,058
- You are out of order!
- Order in the Cabinet!

766
00:39:12,142 --> 00:39:13,142
Instruct the Sergeant-at-Arms

767
00:39:13,268 --> 00:39:14,227
to suppress this!

768
00:39:14,311 --> 00:39:15,436
We are in session!

769
00:39:15,562 --> 00:39:17,522
Please don't encourage this!

