783
00:39:45,926 --> 00:39:46,926
about how they change.

784
00:39:47,511 --> 00:39:48,553
He's here.

785
00:39:48,637 --> 00:39:51,138
He's here! Mrs. Cuthbert, he's here!

786
00:39:51,682 --> 00:39:53,099
- Robbie.
- Hi, Mom.

787
00:39:53,183 --> 00:39:54,517
- Oh, Robbie.
- Hey.

